Package: poistats
Title: Statistical Analysis Tools for Poisson Distributions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Somnath", "Chaudhuri", email = "somnath.chaudhuri@soton.ac.uk", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to generate random Poisson-distributed numbers,
    calculate comprehensive summary statistics, and create visualizations 
    including histograms, boxplots, violin plots, and density plots.
